The special event ran for the whole week, so why are the sales like this?

57
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:31,660
It's because of those "Gu Yeon Jeong shoes" I guess.

58
00:03:31,660 --> 00:03:34,080
What's the use of selling 100 of them for $10,

59
