76
00:04:27,540 --> 00:04:30,000
I will definitely make the launching show a success.

77
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:32,660
Words...

78
00:04:32,660 --> 00:04:36,740
Also, what are you going to do about what happened at the wedding?

79
00:04:36,740 --> 00:04:40,160
Listen, Team Leader Oh. I told you to behave well.

80
00:04:40,160 --> 00:04:44,000
Don't make the people you work with needlessly uncomfortable!

81
