88
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:28,440
Lastly, you should greet the team leader.

89
00:05:28,440 --> 00:05:30,020
Okay.

90
00:05:34,180 --> 00:05:36,400
Team Leader?

91
00:05:40,420 --> 00:05:42,600
