92
00:05:46,280 --> 00:05:50,920
Hello, I'm the new marketing team intern starting today, Gi Seong Jae.

93
00:05:51,780 --> 00:05:53,600
He's a total flower boy, right?

94
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:56,700
