95
00:05:56,700 --> 00:06:01,560
He's dazzling. I think they picked based on looks this time.

96
00:06:03,400 --> 00:06:05,100
Welcome, Gi Seong Jae.

97
00:06:05,100 --> 00:06:08,060
From now on, Assistant Hong will give you directions on work-related things,

98
00:06:08,060 --> 00:06:11,760
