103
00:06:47,620 --> 00:06:50,220
I'm fine.

104
00:07:14,780 --> 00:07:17,020
Take a look at this.

105
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:22,040
Look at this too. This material is very important.

106
00:07:22,040 --> 00:07:24,340
- Ah, yes.
- This and this, please safeguard this.

107
00:07:24,340 --> 00:07:25,520
I've got it.

108
00:07:25,520 --> 00:07:27,660
And this and these materials

109
00:07:27,660 --> 00:07:31,000
