110
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:36,540
Wow, I'm really jealous of you, Sunbae-nim.

111
00:07:36,540 --> 00:07:38,280
All the girls he went on arranged dates with are pretty. All of them!

112
00:07:38,280 --> 00:07:41,060
Eh... they're profile pictures!

113
00:07:41,060 --> 00:07:44,220
