115
00:07:46,180 --> 00:07:47,280
Really?

116
00:07:47,280 --> 00:07:49,520
Then, are you getting married this year, Sunbaenim?

117
00:07:49,520 --> 00:07:51,020
But the thing is,

118
00:07:51,020 --> 00:07:55,480
my mother said nobody wins at everything.

119
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:56,920
What she said is exactly right.

120
00:07:56,920 --> 00:08:01,000
Number 1, Moon Gyu Ri. She's really pretty, but she's a graduate student.

121
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:03,700
