124
00:08:11,280 --> 00:08:14,360
The instability of the retirement makes me nervous. Number 3, Kim Ji Won.

125
00:08:14,360 --> 00:08:17,340
Her personality is good, and she's really pretty but

126
00:08:17,340 --> 00:08:24,040
