127
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:25,700
Wow.

128
00:08:25,700 --> 00:08:27,240
Hello.

129
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:28,560
Hello.

130
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:31,480
Hello.

131
00:08:32,880 --> 00:08:37,140
Sunbae Won likes sweet stuff, so I got you an iced mocha.

132
00:08:37,140 --> 00:08:39,000
Thank you.

133
00:08:42,140 --> 00:08:44,910
- Have this, Sunbae.
- Oh, thank you.

134
00:08:45,700 --> 00:08:47,540
Oh, is this an espresso?

135
00:08:47,540 --> 00:08:49,240
Sunbaenim, you have an ardent love for coffee, right?

136
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:51,020
Oh.

137
00:08:51,020 --> 00:08:54,820
For you, Sunbae Min Guk, it's healthy five grains latte.

138
00:08:54,820 --> 00:08:56,980
Dong Geon Sunbae, a simple Americano.

139
00:08:56,980 --> 00:08:58,560
Oh.

140
00:08:58,560 --> 00:09:01,820
- So Eun, your sense is great!
- She's really something.

141
00:09:01,820 --> 00:09:03,240
- Sunbae?
- Hm?

142
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:04,820
How's a girl with sense?

143
00:09:06,260 --> 00:09:10,400
So Eun's style is not Sunbae Woo Jin's, but Sunbae Won's.

144
00:09:10,400 --> 00:09:11,380
Why?

145
00:09:11,380 --> 00:09:14,520
Isn't it that a positive and negative balance to each other?

146
00:09:14,520 --> 00:09:17,420
For a guy that is cynical and cold like him,

147
00:09:17,420 --> 00:09:20,420
