148
00:09:20,420 --> 00:09:23,360
Sunbae Won, what do you think?

149
00:09:25,160 --> 00:09:26,020
Stop it.

150
00:09:26,020 --> 00:09:28,040
Hey, you like it.

151
00:09:28,040 --> 00:09:34,220
Will this two become an item?

152
00:09:38,900 --> 00:09:41,500
- Sunbaenim! Hello.
- Hello.

153
00:09:41,500 --> 00:09:43,580
Hello.

154
00:09:47,560 --> 00:09:49,880
What is this? I want coffee.

155
00:09:49,880 --> 00:09:52,400
- Here, coffee.
- Coffee.

156
00:09:55,620 --> 00:09:56,440
I'll be back!

157
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:58,160
Yes.

158
00:10:10,230 --> 00:10:13,910
