162
00:10:31,060 --> 00:10:36,240
Ahh, you remember it now! The department store, right?

163
00:10:37,180 --> 00:10:40,900
I've been wanting to thank you because I couldn't thank you back then.

164
00:10:40,900 --> 00:10:43,400
But we meet again like this.

165
00:10:43,400 --> 00:10:48,300
Right! To be honest, I thought you were my age.

166
00:10:48,300 --> 00:10:53,400
So, I was going to hit on you when we met this morning.

167
00:10:56,280 --> 00:11:02,140
No, no! Please don't get me wrong! I am just saying I thought you were my age.

168
00:11:02,140 --> 00:11:05,680
Anyway, I will work diligently from now on.

169
00:11:05,680 --> 00:11:09,290
I really wanted to work in fashion marketing.

170
00:11:16,420 --> 00:11:19,550
Unni, how can you go back and forth with the main DP (display)?

171
00:11:19,550 --> 00:11:21,930
There's still a week before the vacation season starts.

172
00:11:21,930 --> 00:11:24,990
Until then we should display ladies shoes.

173
00:11:24,990 --> 00:11:29,350
Team Leader Oh, I am about to die too. Do you see the multi-shop in front?

174
00:11:29,350 --> 00:11:31,270
They sell shoes as well.

175
00:11:31,270 --> 00:11:33,890
On top of that, the ace quit last week.

176
00:11:33,890 --> 00:11:37,150
What can we do? We have to display the most popular items.

177
00:11:37,150 --> 00:11:38,830
Who is the president here?

178
00:11:38,830 --> 00:11:41,030
Tell him to come out at once!

179
00:11:41,030 --> 00:11:45,790
She is back again. We can't increase revenue when we get that sort of customer.

180
00:11:45,790 --> 00:11:47,380
Yes, Customer!

181
00:11:47,380 --> 00:11:49,330
I'll take care of her.

182
00:11:50,510 --> 00:11:51,620
What brought you here?

183
00:11:51,620 --> 00:11:54,240
Are you in charge of this store?

184
00:11:54,240 --> 00:11:55,800
Yes.

185
00:11:56,860 --> 00:11:58,980
Refund me right away!

186
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:15,120
Because you wore these shoes for too long, we can't refund you.

187
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:19,900
I am asking for a refund! I can't wear them because they are restricting my feet.

188
00:12:19,900 --> 00:12:23,030
What parts of your feet are being restricted?

189
00:12:23,030 --> 00:12:26,730
Are you saying I am lying?

190
00:12:26,730 --> 00:12:29,600
Please excuse me for a minute.

191
00:12:32,670 --> 00:12:35,480
-Uhh! Omo, omo!
-Just a minute.

192
00:12:35,480 --> 00:12:39,420
Huh? What are you doing?

193
00:12:40,920 --> 00:12:44,260
The top of your foot is slightly higher than average.

194
00:12:46,620 --> 00:12:49,640
The front of your foot is thinner compared to the back of your foot.

195
00:12:49,640 --> 00:12:54,160
You put more pressure on the front when you walk so your toes hurt too.

196
00:13:03,780 --> 00:13:05,500
Here.

197
00:13:10,400 --> 00:13:13,750
We'll adjust your shoes to fit the shape of your feet.

198
00:13:13,750 --> 00:13:18,770
If they are still uncomfortable after the repair, then we'll give you a refund.

199
00:13:27,590 --> 00:13:29,450
Thank you!

200
00:13:31,450 --> 00:13:38,350
