Let's redo the DP (Display).

203
00:13:53,670 --> 00:14:01,230
Fine! Then work at the store for three hours every day until we find the ace. Okay!

204
00:14:01,230 --> 00:14:04,370
Fine! But you'll do the DP yourself, Team Leader Oh.

205
00:14:04,370 --> 00:14:06,610
Understood!

206
00:14:12,820 --> 00:14:15,660
Wow, you were so persuasive earlier!

207
00:14:15,660 --> 00:14:19,790
Sometimes it works better if you persuade physically.

208
00:14:19,790 --> 00:14:24,270
The more I see you, the more charming you are, Team Leader.

209
00:14:24,270 --> 00:14:26,790
I think I'll be completely smitten with you.

210
00:14:28,550 --> 00:14:31,430
Here!

211
00:14:32,610 --> 00:14:34,390
Okay.

212
00:15:30,580 --> 00:15:31,750
You are still here?

213
00:15:31,750 --> 00:15:34,670
Yes, I was waiting for you.

214
00:15:41,130 --> 00:15:43,990
It's dangerous for a woman to stay alone.

215
00:15:48,170 --> 00:15:50,610
I'll be right there until you finish.

216
00:15:50,610 --> 00:15:53,350
Call me any time if you need me.

217
00:16:08,630 --> 00:16:11,390
Is it because he's from the younger generation?

218
00:16:11,390 --> 00:16:13,710
- How old is he?
- Huh?

219
00:16:13,710 --> 00:16:17,070
He was born in 90, so 26 years old?

220
00:16:17,070 --> 00:16:18,590
He's still a kiddo.

221
00:16:18,590 --> 00:16:22,410
That's what I am saying. But he doesn't seem to be uncomfortable with me.

222
00:16:22,410 --> 00:16:25,010
He was waiting for me earlier while I worked overtime.

223
00:16:25,010 --> 00:16:26,630
You know what he said to me?

224
00:16:26,630 --> 00:16:29,250
It's dangerous for a woman to stay alone.

225
00:16:30,110 --> 00:16:31,230
Isn't it funny?

226
00:16:31,230 --> 00:16:33,700
The punk has social skills.

227
00:16:33,700 --> 00:16:35,020
That's what I am saying.

228
00:16:35,020 --> 00:16:37,020
So what did you tell him?

229
00:16:37,020 --> 00:16:44,040
Not sure. Under my normal circumstances I'd have scolded him.

230
00:16:44,700 --> 00:16:47,020
But strangely, I let it go.

231
00:16:47,020 --> 00:16:49,960
Hey! Why would you go that far?

232
00:16:49,960 --> 00:16:50,630
Huh?

233
00:16:50,630 --> 00:16:51,960
