234
00:16:51,960 --> 00:16:55,940
The possibility of that kiddo seeing you as a woman is less than one percent.

235
00:16:55,940 --> 00:17:00,520
Don't overreact by the intern's lip service, Oh Ha Na. Huh?

236
00:17:00,520 --> 00:17:02,350
Are you jealous?

237
00:17:02,350 --> 00:17:03,150
What?

238
00:17:03,150 --> 00:17:06,950
You are not popular among your female juniors because you are too stiff and boring.

239
00:17:06,950 --> 00:17:10,090
You are just envious because I am loved by the intern, huh?

240
00:17:10,090 --> 00:17:11,570
That's why you are dissing me right now, right?

241
00:17:11,570 --> 00:17:13,150
Hey, I am very popular!

242
00:17:13,150 --> 00:17:14,050
As if!

243
00:17:14,050 --> 00:17:16,110
I am telling you I am. You want to come by tomorrow and see it?

244
00:17:16,110 --> 00:17:18,790
Never mind! Let's hang up!

245
00:17:25,330 --> 00:17:27,410
Sunbae!

246
00:17:48,430 --> 00:17:54,760
Thank you, for helping me on the last flight. I didn't know what to do with that customer.

247
00:17:54,760 --> 00:17:57,100
You saved me, Sunbae.

248
00:17:57,100 --> 00:17:59,850
It's nothing.

249
00:17:59,850 --> 00:18:03,990
No, it was very important to me.

250
00:18:03,990 --> 00:18:10,870
I actually wanted to use that incident (as an excuse) to have a meal with you.

251
00:18:11,970 --> 00:18:13,790
Can't we?

252
00:18:18,190 --> 00:18:23,390
You are not popular among your female juniors because you are too stiff and boring.

253
00:18:25,370 --> 00:18:27,330
Shall we?

254
00:18:30,890 --> 00:18:33,110
Thank you.

255
00:18:35,770 --> 00:18:38,940
Finally I get to have a meal with you!

256
00:18:49,120 --> 00:18:53,920
It's a Fukuoka specialty. You cook it like this and eat it.

257
00:18:56,340 --> 00:18:58,700
Here! Ah!

258
